reviewText: Excellent story, well acted, and a charming ending.
I like the actress so I bought the movie. I was expecting more out of the movie, a little disappointed.

This movie is full of intrigue and suspense.  It's a film that makes you think; it's a movie you find yourself participating in.

Poppy Montgomery is great in the lead role of Nadine.

Highly recommend.
Between was a great DVD movie which I ordered new; it arrived timely; I watched it; because I'm in the process of moving, I don't have too much more to say, except, kudos!Between
